{"tid":2373144,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【播毒失敗】中国人喝醉闖北韓邊境 遭開槍擊斃","createTime":"2021-01-20T08:37:26.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-20T15:40:29.000Z","uid":293677,"like":880,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":96,"replies":[{"pid":"a314f825b04fae52c5274fea4e4ed8b5c0de1011","tid":2373144,"uid":293677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:37:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"xx-large\"><ins>中國人喝醉闖邊境 遭北韓士兵開槍擊斃</ins></span><br />\n<br />\n2021/01/20 14:48<br />\n<br />\n〔即時新聞／綜合報導〕武漢肺炎（新型冠狀病毒病，COVID-19）疫情在全球蔓延，北韓宣稱境內零確診，同時關閉邊界以防病毒傳入，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">傳出有1名中國人喝醉後越境進入北韓，遭邊防士兵擊斃。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n據《朝鮮日報》報導，<span class=\"red\"><span class=\"x-large\">當地時間14日傍晚6點，1名約50歲的中國男子在喝醉後，從中國東北遼寧省集安市走到鴨綠江滑冰，不知不覺越境進入北韓，遭到北韓邊防士兵擊斃，擊斃該男子後，北韓方面將遺體送還給中國。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n報導指出，槍擊事件發生後北韓與中國兩方都在邊境地區加強了警戒，北韓宣稱境內零確診，同時關閉邊界以防病毒傳入，去年5月、7月都曾發生過類似事件，已經至少3人因此死亡；韓媒認為，隨著北韓嚴格控制邊境，恐成為與中國之間爆發外交問題的隱憂。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3416728\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3416728&d=6tm4WXRLZYcZc%2BeJmW1Ia%2FG%2BV2qV11Yco%2FuAlnZU2is%3D&h=32af1d96\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fworld%2Fbreakingnews%2F3416728&h=b9b8712d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/3416728</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><span class=\"limegreen\">中国特工想去北韓播毒？</span>"},{"pid":"46ab376d457b59b9b98db5abc37ebf37c2910aed","tid":2373144,"uid":38904,"like":134,"dislike":2,"score":132,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:38:29.000Z","msg":"打! 往死裏打!<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/clean.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"962c26adb45e40daa3e0f99e6ace3eabc03545f3","tid":2373144,"uid":293677,"like":404,"dislike":4,"score":400,"citedBy":7,"replyTime":"2021-01-20T08:39:02.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>擊斃該男子後，北韓方面將遺體送還給中國。</blockqu